- READ:  {"type": "read_workboard"}
- EDIT:  {"type": "edit_workboard", "old_text": "- [ ] 1: ...", "new_text": "- [x] 1: Done"}
- APPEND: {"type": "edit_workboard", "append": "## Results\nFindings here..."}
When a workboard exists: read it first, do your task, then edit it to mark your subtask done and record results.

